== Nehemias achem [[Pustok]] ==
'''Book of Nehemiah'''

'''Nehemiasachem Pustok char bhagamnim vanttum ieta ː''' 

'''1.''' Nehemiasachem Jerusaleak portonnem. Persiechea razan Judacher razvottki cholounk taka thoim dhaddlolo.

'''2.''' Jerusaleachim durgam novean bandtat.

'''3.''' Ezra Devachi Somurt vhoddlean ani dobajean porjek vachta ani porza aplem patok vollkhun gheta

'''4.''' Judacho rajpak koso Nehemiasacho fuddlo vavr.

Hea pustokachi kheritai mhollear Nehemiasacho khol bhavarth vacher ani portun-portun Devak kel'lem tachem magnnem.


'''Hea pustokacho attap ː'''


Nehemias Jerusaleak portotat  1/1 - 2/20

Jerusaleachim durgam novean bandtat 3/1 - 7/73

Somurt vachtat ani Korar novsortat 8/1 - 10/39

Nehemiasacheo fuddleo kariavolli 11/1 - 13/31

